<p>Hey there! Welcome to my little corner of the internet. I'm Uwni, and this is where I document my adventures
  through cyberspace, share technical discoveries, and explore what it means to exist digitally.</p>

<h2>Recent Posts</h2>

<div class="post-list">
  <article webc:for="post of collections.posts.reverse()" class="post-list-item">
    <h3 class="post-list-title">
      <a :href="post.url" @text="post.data.title"></a>
    </h3>
    <div class="post-list-meta">
      <time @text="post.data.date"></time>
      <span webc:if="post.data.tags"> â€¢ Tags:
        <span webc:for="tag of post.data.tags">
          <a :href="`/tags/${tag}/`" @text="`#${tag}`"></a>
        </span>
      </span>
    </div>
    <div class="post-list-excerpt" @text="(post.data.description || post.data.title || '').substring(0, 200) + (post.data.description && post.data.description.length > 200 ? '...' : '')"></div>
  </article>
</div>

<h2>About This Space</h2>

<p>This blog is built with <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/">Eleventy</a> and <a href="https://typst.app/">Typst</a>,
  combining the power of modern static site generation with beautiful typography. Each post exists as both HTML for
  the web and PDF for offline reading.</p>

<p>Feel free to explore, and don't hesitate to reach out if something resonates with you!</p>

